cvxclustr 1.1.1
========================

* Added Makevars and Makevars.win to handle BLAS calls in C code.
* Updated license to CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 to better suit CRAN's distribution.

cvxclustr 1.1.0
========================

* Functions added for computing cluster assignments.
* Function added for choosing bigger AMA step-sizes.
* Functions added for computing Gaussian kernel, k-nearest neighbor, and combination weights.

cvxclustr 1.0.0
========================

* Package release.
